      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Changes from the commitment in the plans need to be assessed in terms of the impact on the funding of resources and the bottom-line forecast.  Calculate various items to determine degree of reasoning in the numbers for such items as previous run rates versus next period run rates; head count modifications on operational shifts; direct and indirect overhead spending and variance, etc.  Also calculate the impact of capital additions/roll-offs and their depreciation."/>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-approvedby" metaValue="[&quot;Tames, Daniela&quot;]"/>
